-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-Gallagher.-CREDIT_-Alvaro-Ballesteros_Europa-Press-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>反悔了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲乐队</a>目前正在录制一张新专辑的说法，并告诉歌迷“这很有趣”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">支持我：2025 年绿洲阵容中的所有球员</a></strong></li></ul><p>自从今年早些时候英国流行音乐偶像宣布他们的首次重聚演出以来，他们将自 2009 年以来首次一起现场表演，利亚姆一直开玩笑说，即将举行的不仅仅是一场巡演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/is-liam-gallagher-teasing-us-with-a-new-oasis-album-its-already-finished-3791619">九月份，当一位粉丝问</a>“绿洲真的会有新专辑吗？？？”时，利亚姆回答说：“是的，已经完成了。”他还回答了一位粉丝询问新唱片是否“正在酝酿之中”的问题，他回答说：“它已经在袋子里了，伙计，操他妈的空气”。</p><p>然后，本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-teases-that-hes-blown-away-by-music-noel-has-written-for-new-oasis-album-3809373">他在 Twitter/X 上告诉粉丝，诺埃尔为记录而写的材料让他“震惊”</a> 。在宣布复出后，他在四月份发表的评论也再次出现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-oasis-about-to-record-a-new-album-fans-have-some-theories-3788575">他在其中暗示 Oasis 将在 11 月份录制一张新专辑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809656" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809656" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809656" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Liam-and-Noel-Gallagher-perform-as-Oasis.-CREDIT_-Dave-Hogan_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809656" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺尔·加拉格尔饰演绿洲。图片来源：戴夫·霍根/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>虽然利亚姆在 X/Twitter 上以轻松和轻率而闻名，而且他的推文远没有得到任何官方证实，但他确实有在新闻成为公众所知之前泄露线索的形式，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-seemingly-teases-oasis-reunion-tour-announcement-date-3786858">最初取笑了乐队的重聚</a>，他们的英国和爱尔兰 2025 年巡演日期<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">均在官方确认之前</a>。</p><p>但现在，他驳回了之前的预告片，称“没有正在制作中的绿洲专辑”。利亚姆在回应粉丝新闻报道称兄弟俩正在“专心致志”制作新专辑时说：“我他妈是在开玩笑，记住他们，原因是因为这些天每个人都有点紧张，如果我感到不安，我很抱歉除了我以外，任何人都觉得这很有趣。”</p><p>然后，在回应一位粉丝说重聚“足够了”时，利亚姆写道：“正是人们总是想要更多，让我们进入一个大体育场，然后看看你和我在一起之后会发生什么或者什么”。他还回复了一位粉丝的“为什么不呢？”，并写道：“我很忙”。</p><blockquo